# Project Name: Image Search

## Description:
The Image Search project is designed to provide users with a convenient way to search for images based on specific keywords or tags. It utilizes a search algorithm to retrieve relevant images from a database or external sources and displays them in a user-friendly interface.

## Features:
- Keyword-based image search
- Tag-based image search
- Image filtering and sorting options
- User authentication and authorization
- Image upload and management
- Image metadata extraction
- Image preview and download options
- Responsive design for different devices

